      "prompt": "A portion of the slope field of the differential equation is given. Sketch the solution curve through the point $(0, 1)$.",
      "point_value": 1,
      "scoring_notes": "From scoring key: Curve must pass through $(0,1)$ and follow slope field. The equilibrium solution is $y = 3$; curves starting below $y = 3$ approach it from below.",
